nal time-dependent forcing term.\n- `params[2]*x1`: linear spring force component.\n- `params[3]*x1^3`: nonlinear spring force component.\n- `params[4]*x2`: damping proportional to velocity.\n\nThis skeleton captures the essential physics of a damped nonlinear oscillator. You can fit parameters to data accordingly.']
